        <property propertyId="38f94dd1-d5aa-41b8-b182-c0c42985d9dc" amount="0.55" unitId="7b75baf0-cbee-45e6-bf66-af119da06553">
          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. This price is averaged from 3 different suppliers available in the commercial webstore of alibaba. The price refers to a bulk quantity purchase. All websites were retrieved on the 19th Sept 2017. THe exchange rate used is from 2010 when 1 USD - 0.755 EUR.
Price range: 
supplier 1: 500-800 $ per ton, https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Made-in-China-white-powder-D_60722176880.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.1.3c93b095noQeHG
supplier 2: 0.1-1,080 $ per ton, https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Chemical-reagent-high-purity-Glucose_60726433628.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.33.3c93b095noQeHG&amp;s=p
supplier 3: 400-600 $ per ton,  https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Beverage-industry-pure-glucose_60680201154.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.41.3c93b095noQeHG&amp;s=p</comment>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="a9358458-9724-4f03-b622-106eda248916" amount="0.0" isDefiningValue="false" unitId="577e242a-461f-44a7-922c-d8e1c3d2bf45">
